  <display_name>Upgrade Wall Insulation</display_name>
  <description>This measure upgrades all exterior wall constructions by applying a user-specified insulation R-value (R-10, R-15, R-20, or R-25).</description>
  <modeler_description>Creates a new single-layer massless construction and applies it to exterior walls. Uses IP R-value input converted to SI units for simulation.</modeler_description>
